  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Veterans referred for cardiac rehabilitation at the VA Boston Healthcare System.

          -  Moderate to severe OSA (AHI &gt;15) on home sleep testing.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Dangerous levels of sleepiness (Epworth Sleepiness Scale score &gt;16 or a report of
             falling asleep at the wheel of a car within the past 2 years).

          -  Physical limitation precluding exercise testing.
      </textblock>
